org.cougaar.planning.ldm.plan
Interface AllocationResultDistributor

All Superinterfaces:
AspectType
All Known Implementing Classes:
AllocationResultDistributor.DefaultDistributor
public interface AllocationResultDistributor
extends AspectType

AllocationResultDistributor is a class which specifies how allocation results should be distributed amongst 'parent' tasks of a Composition. Distributes all aspect values amongst all parent tasks, divides COST and QUANTITY aspects evenly among all parent tasks. Distributes all AuxiliaryQueryTypes and data to all parent tasks.

See Also:
AllocationResult
